<h1 id="lab-using-the-python-debugger-pdb">Lab: Using the Python
Debugger (<code>pdb</code>)</h1>
<h2 id="steps">Steps</h2>
<ol type="1">
<li><strong>Import the pdb module</strong></li>
</ol>
<div class="sourceCode" id="cb1"><pre
class="sourceCode python"><code class="sourceCode python"><span id="cb1-1"><a href="#cb1-1" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="im">import</span> pdb</span></code></pre></div>
<ol start="2" type="1">
<li><p><strong>Set a breakpoint</strong> Insert
<code>pdb.set_trace()</code> where you want to start debugging.</p></li>
<li><p><strong>Run your script</strong> Execute your Python script as
usual. The debugger will pause at the breakpoint.</p></li>
<li><p><strong>Use pdb commands</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><code>n</code>: Next line</li>
<li><code>c</code>: Continue execution</li>
<li><code>l</code>: List source code</li>
<li><code>p &lt;variable&gt;</code>: Print variable value</li>
<li><code>q</code>: Quit debugger</li>
</ul></li>
</ol>
<h2 id="example">Example</h2>
<div class="sourceCode" id="cb2"><pre
class="sourceCode python"><code class="sourceCode python"><span id="cb2-1"><a href="#cb2-1" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="kw">def</span> add(a, b):</span>
<span id="cb2-2"><a href="#cb2-2" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>     <span class="im">import</span> pdb<span class="op">;</span> pdb.set_trace()  <span class="co"># Set a breakpoint here</span></span>
<span id="cb2-3"><a href="#cb2-3" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>     result <span class="op">=</span> a <span class="op">+</span> b</span>
<span id="cb2-4"><a href="#cb2-4" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>     <span class="cf">return</span> result</span>
<span id="cb2-5"><a href="#cb2-5" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a></span>
<span id="cb2-6"><a href="#cb2-6" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>x <span class="op">=</span> <span class="dv">5</span></span>
<span id="cb2-7"><a href="#cb2-7" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>y <span class="op">=</span> <span class="dv">7</span></span>
<span id="cb2-8"><a href="#cb2-8" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="bu">print</span>(add(x, y))</span></code></pre></div>
<p><strong>How to run:</strong></p>
<div class="sourceCode" id="cb3"><pre
class="sourceCode bash"><code class="sourceCode bash"><span id="cb3-1"><a href="#cb3-1" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="ex">python</span> your_script.py</span></code></pre></div>
<p>When execution reaches <code>pdb.set_trace()</code>, you'll enter the
interactive debugger and can inspect variables or step through the
code.</p>
